des:
With the official SAWT Sydney Skill, you can hear your favorite radio right now on Alexa! 

SAWT Sydney was established in January, 2020, as an Arabic online radio station with top hits, and live shows that originate in Sydney for the world to hear. SAWT Sydney is rocking the traditional sound of Arabic radio, giving a unique Arabic voice. SAWT Sydney is the voice for the voiceless. Come and enjoy the soul of Lebanon. SAWT Sydney will be the bridge to connect Australia to Lebanon, as well as, all Middle Eastern countries. SAWT Sydney will feature all types of interviews, with many stars and influential individuals ranging from entertainment and political segments to discussion regarding important issues. SAWT Sydney, Be Real, Be Simple.
